videos.description: Deandre Burnett hits his 4th 3-pointer as Ole Miss takes a 21-15 lead.
videos.headline: Ole'Miss' Burnett drains the 3-pointer

videos.description: Frankie Hughes draws the defenders and feeds KJ Walton for the dunk.
videos.headline: Walton finishes nice pass with the dunk

videos.description: Rasheed Brooks hits the off balance 3-pointer from the wing.
videos.headline: Ole Miss' Brooks drains the deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Deandre Burnett takes it strong to the hole and finishes with the layup as Ole Miss takes a 41-30 lead.
videos.headline: Burnett drives to the hoop for the layup

videos.description: Cullen Neal makes the long 3-pointer to give Ole Miss a 12 point lead late in the 1st half.
videos.headline: Neal hits the deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Ole Miss head coach Andy Kennedy can't hear over the band.
videos.headline: Ole Miss head coach Andy Kennedy can't hear a thing

videos.description: Kevin Puryear powers in for the dunk.

videos.description: Marcanvis Hymon and Terrence Phillips mix it up.
videos.headline: Game getting physical

videos.description: Terence Davis blows by the defense and hits the floater to give the Rebels' a 77-64 lead.
videos.headline: Davis drives to the hoop and makes the floater

videos.description: Ole Miss head coach Andy Kennedy talks about the performance of Deandre Burnett against the Tigers.
videos.headline: Andy Kennedy discusses Rebels' win over Missouri
